===Noun Phrase===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[bovine]] [[spongiform]] [[encephalopathy]]'''  (abbreviated as ''[[BSE]]'')

#A fatal, neurodegenerative disease of cattle, which is transmissable to humans through misshaped [[prion]] proteins, caused by eating infected [[tissue]]s.

====Synonyms====
*[[mad cow disease]]
*[[variant Creutzfelt-Jakob disease]]

====Hypernym====
*[[transmissible spongiform encephalopathy]]

